text: My Boyfriend Is an Angel () is a 2012 Russian comedy movie directed by Vera Storozheva. It stars Artur Smolyaninov, Anna Starshenbaum, Sergey Puskepalis, Nikita Efremov and Irina Khakamada. == Other websites == * Category:2012 comedy movies Category:Russian comedy movies
title: My Boyfriend Is an Angel
